{"tid":841958,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來飼養兔仔可令人心境平靜！🌟","createTime":"2018-09-30T02:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T02:52:26.000Z","uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3526b823f95af322aba746cd270b00eef9a2da4f","tid":841958,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:15:40.000Z","msg":"兔子是其中一種最心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們尤其是咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是兔子的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響的。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n以下video可看到兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人！☺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=CMZvBETLpSXbKaXFH7%2BYuTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=0d5f7910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a><br />\n<br />\n當兔子跳兔子舞(Binky)時, 這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活，因為兔子Binky是兔子最開心的狀態。以下video可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=CMZvBETLpSXbKaXFH7%2BYuTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=56c6c5be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">N.B.: </span>實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>參觀然後領養</strong></span>，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=CMZvBETLpSXbKaXFH7%2BYuTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=a931e7a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"578383c59a8ef0fceb619304eb277601ca9e8ca9","tid":841958,"uid":42473,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:19:56.000Z","msg":"你開3個post做乜9"},{"pid":"d0732db9e70fd9cb6b16fe9fe59564ea17d01dc6","tid":841958,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"狗強<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/